== Itabi ry'umwotsi ==[[File:Nicotiana.jpg|thumb|Nicotiana]]
Itabi ni kimwe mu biyobyabwenge banywa cyangwa se basohora umwotsi.

[[Itabi]] rikorwa hifashishishijwe ibibabi ,abahanga mu by'ubuzima bavuga ko

Muri ikigihe hariho ubwoko burenga 70 bw'itabi<ref>https://umutihealth.com/kunywa-itabi/</ref> . mu [[Rwanda]] nahandi kw'Isi.

== Ingaruka ziterwa n'itabi ==
kunywa itabi byangiza mu buryo bukomeye bitewe n'uko umwotsi w'itabi 

habamo ikinyabutabire kitwa [[Itabi|nikotine]],ifite ubushobozi bwo kwangiza 

uturemangingo twubatse [[ubwonko]], ndetse bukangiza ubushobozi bwo gufata 

Abahanga bavuga ko [[Itabi|nikotine]] ihagarika ubudahangarwa bwo kurema 

uturemangingo dusimbura utwangiritse.<ref>https://agakiza.org/Waruziko-kunywa-itabi-byangiza-ingingo-zose-zubatse-umuntu.html</ref>

Ikindi ni ko abanywi b'itabi bigabanyiriza

Imyaka 14 yo kubaho ugereranije n'abatarinywa.

ku banywi [[Igikamba (itabi)|b'itabi]] barimenyereye ntabwo arikuntu cyoroshye guhita barireka burundu.

bisaba cyane kuba umuntu afite ubushake bukomeye

bwo kurireka mbere ya byose<ref>https://dusabane.wordpress.com/2017/06/02/waruziko-ushobora-kubona-umuti-utuma-ucika-burundu-ku-itabi-n-urumugi/</ref>

== Kunywera itabi mu ruhame ==



Nyuma y'indwara zikomeye zihitana imbaga y'abatuye [[isi]], zirimo ibyorezo n'indwara zidakira nka [[SIDA|Sida]] y'isasira ubuzima n'imbaga y'abatuye [[isi]], Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima Ryemezako itabi ari kimwe mu biteza abatuye isi kwibasirwa n'indwara zikomeye z'ihitana imbaga z'abatuye mu [[Rwanda]] nahandi hose kw'isi.

Miriyoni 6 nibo bapfa bariguze bakarinywa, naho abasaga ibihumbi 890 bicwa n'ingaruka ziterwa  

No guhumeka umwotsi w'itabi rinywewe mu ruhame, nu kuvugako ushobora kwicwa n'ingaruka z'itabi ariko utarinywa, ahubwo bigaterwa n'uko w'icaranye n'umuntu uri kurinywa, aba baturage kandi bapfa batarageza kumyaka 70 y'amavuko.<ref>https://isangostar.rw/amakuru/mu-rwanda/article/mu-bushakashatsi-bwakozwe-na-oms</ref>

